WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 7=

01:49.410 --> 01:50.620
You haven't rested well lately.

01:51.410 --> 01:52.250
Today,

01:52.660 --> 01:53.740
you should rest easy.

01:56.570 --> 01:58.460
You usually do housework?

01:59.930 --> 02:02.260
Just some small chores.

02:03.490 --> 02:05.460
I thought the Young Master
of the demon sect

02:06.210 --> 02:07.850
lived in luxury,

02:07.930 --> 02:08.890
with servants

02:09.340 --> 02:10.660
at his beck and call.

02:10.940 --> 02:11.993
You read it in a storybook?

02:13.730 --> 02:14.820
Father doesn't like noise.

02:16.410 --> 02:17.690
He told me

02:18.260 --> 02:19.660
that cleaning every inch

02:20.010 --> 02:21.380
of his room

02:21.850 --> 02:22.890
and organizing every book

02:23.060 --> 02:24.100
he's read

02:24.730 --> 02:25.570
was immensely joyful.

02:25.980 --> 02:26.820
Your father is

02:28.220 --> 02:30.220
not quite the man

02:30.220 --> 02:31.060
I imagined.

02:33.410 --> 02:35.170
In the stories,

02:36.220 --> 02:37.060
all the Mus

02:37.290 --> 02:38.820
are bloodthirsty villains.

02:45.010 --> 02:45.850
Where's Qian Xueshen?

02:46.190 --> 02:47.030
Don't worry.

02:47.060 --> 02:48.400
He has a whole group serving him.

02:48.980 --> 02:50.130
Right now,

02:50.380 --> 02:51.540
it should be quite lively.

02:56.850 --> 02:57.690
We're both guests.

02:57.940 --> 02:59.260
Why is the treatment so different?

03:03.780 --> 03:04.620
Mu,

03:05.100 --> 03:06.540
how can you treat me like this?

03:08.890 --> 03:09.983
The journey through the snow

03:10.096 --> 03:11.820
is not as simple
as walking down the street

03:11.820 --> 03:13.260
to buy a box of rouge.

03:14.940 --> 03:15.940
This lawless land

03:16.610 --> 03:17.450
has fierce customs.

03:18.010 --> 03:18.850
It's very dangerous.

03:19.170 --> 03:20.940
One misstep could lead to a trap.

03:21.220 --> 03:22.380
This place is so dangerous.

03:22.730 --> 03:23.570
I think

03:24.450 --> 03:25.540
I should go with you.

03:25.940 --> 03:26.780
Lately,

03:27.260 --> 03:29.730
you've risked enough for me.

03:30.540 --> 03:31.380
Besides,

03:31.610 --> 03:33.850
isn't Nie Zhe clearing out
the Mu remnants?

03:34.130 --> 03:35.340
You'd better stay out of sight.

03:37.850 --> 03:38.890
Zhao, are you worried

03:39.890 --> 03:40.730
about me?

03:42.220 --> 03:44.100
I just think Nie Zhe is detestable.

03:46.290 --> 03:47.130
By the way,

03:51.060 --> 03:52.540
why did your Li Sect end up

03:52.780 --> 03:54.410
with the Nie clan?

03:56.340 --> 03:58.380
My great-grandfather
adopted Nie Hengcheng.

03:58.946 --> 04:00.260
He later assisted my grandfather.

04:00.570 --> 04:01.493
Grandfather died young.

04:01.820 --> 04:03.660
At that time, Father was not yet ten,

04:04.220 --> 04:06.130
so Nie Hengcheng took over the sect

04:06.620 --> 04:07.610
until Father came of age.

04:08.380 --> 04:10.130
But Father had no interest in power,

04:10.690 --> 04:12.540
so Nie Hengcheng kept running the sect,

04:13.170 --> 04:15.340
eventually taking it as his own.

04:16.290 --> 04:18.370
What kind of person is Nie Hengcheng

04:19.340 --> 04:20.290
that my aunt

04:21.050 --> 04:22.460
would risk her life to kill him?

04:23.100 --> 04:24.290
Nie Hengcheng is talented

04:24.460 --> 04:25.379
and rare in the world.

04:26.170 --> 04:27.610
To the Six Sects,

04:27.660 --> 04:28.810
he's a demon.

04:29.580 --> 04:30.460
But in our sect,

04:31.340 --> 04:32.730
he is a pillar of the world,

04:33.580 --> 04:34.490
an unshakable anchor.

04:36.540 --> 04:37.460
Then why did he

04:37.700 --> 04:38.930
go against all rules,

04:39.020 --> 04:40.046
killing without restraint?

04:40.540 --> 04:41.780
That's because later

04:41.850 --> 04:43.540
he mastered a supreme skill

04:46.540 --> 04:48.250
that was called the Ziwei Method

04:48.460 --> 04:49.930
and was created by the Mu ancestors.

04:50.460 --> 04:51.700
This method

04:51.780 --> 04:52.730
was powerful

04:52.730 --> 04:53.780
and invincible,

04:54.490 --> 04:55.700
but long lost.

04:55.810 --> 04:57.259
Later, Nie Hengcheng somehow acquired

04:57.270 --> 04:58.490
its cultivation method,

04:58.700 --> 05:00.540
and it became the root of all disasters.

05:00.610 --> 05:02.250
Father told me about this skill.

05:02.660 --> 05:04.020
He said such a defiant skill

05:04.340 --> 05:05.410
must have hidden dangers;

05:05.619 --> 05:06.799
better not to practice at all.

05:08.850 --> 05:10.580
Your father is
truly a man of detachment.

05:11.460 --> 05:12.300
I've always wondered:

05:13.540 --> 05:14.930
If Father weren't so detached

05:16.100 --> 05:18.220
and hadn't handed over
the Chief position,

05:18.730 --> 05:20.310
how many lives

05:20.320 --> 05:21.340
would have changed?

05:22.580 --> 05:24.460
Wu Yuanying wouldn't have suffered

05:24.460 --> 05:25.580
for ten years.

05:27.050 --> 05:28.100
Ms. Cai Pingshu

05:28.700 --> 05:29.850
wouldn't have died so early.

05:31.250 --> 05:32.410
It's not his fault.

05:34.900 --> 05:36.810
He simply didn't want to go
against his heart.

05:37.490 --> 05:38.540
My aunt was like that, too.

05:39.980 --> 05:41.250
She was bold and fearless

05:42.460 --> 05:45.410
but afraid of being trapped at home.

05:46.540 --> 05:47.930
Perhaps the same applies

05:48.540 --> 05:49.380
to your father.

05:50.540 --> 05:51.380
Your father

05:51.700 --> 05:53.050
must be a very good man.

05:53.850 --> 05:54.780
Otherwise, Uncle Chang

05:54.780 --> 05:57.206
wouldn't trust you so easily
after a single act of kindness.

05:57.930 --> 05:59.276
It must be because of your father

05:59.660 --> 06:00.810
that he believes

06:01.810 --> 06:02.776
you're not a bad person.

06:04.980 --> 06:05.820
Zhao...

06:12.250 --> 06:13.090
What's wrong?

06:35.220 --> 06:36.060
Thank you.

06:56.660 --> 06:58.133
(Uncle Cheng, Li Sect)
Young Master,

06:58.144 --> 06:59.889
you weren't affected
by the sleeping powder,

06:59.900 --> 07:02.050
so why let Miss Cai go?

07:06.370 --> 07:07.580
To cheer her up.

07:45.660 --> 07:46.610
What a worthless bird.

07:47.020 --> 07:48.266
It probably follows its master.

07:50.780 --> 07:52.100
It's about to snow.

07:52.780 --> 07:53.900
This place is so remote.

07:54.780 --> 07:56.250
Is there somewhere to stay?

08:40.770 --> 08:41.610
Ma'am,

08:41.650 --> 08:42.700
we're here to stay.

08:45.060 --> 08:46.130
Miss,

08:46.770 --> 08:47.700
may I ask your name?

08:49.650 --> 08:50.490
I'm Feng Xiaohan.

08:50.770 --> 08:52.100
This is my...

08:52.610 --> 08:53.450
Well.

08:53.650 --> 08:54.980
My fiancé,

08:55.650 --> 08:56.490
Wan Dazhuang.

08:56.650 --> 08:57.490
Wan...

08:59.300 --> 09:00.580
Since you two are a couple,

09:03.580 --> 09:04.580
Blooming Flowers

09:04.770 --> 09:06.340
is our best room.

09:06.610 --> 09:07.850
It has a soft animal-skin bed

09:07.850 --> 09:08.700
and fine bedding,

09:09.130 --> 09:10.670
and the back door leads to hot springs.

09:10.850 --> 09:11.730
Very romantic.

09:12.420 --> 09:13.420
Payment

09:14.300 --> 09:15.180
can be settled later

09:15.580 --> 09:17.220
at checkout.

09:18.610 --> 09:20.300
I didn't expect such attentive service

09:20.530 --> 09:22.340
(Blooming Flowers)
in this harsh, cold land.

09:22.490 --> 09:24.060
Right, Dazhuang?

09:27.530 --> 09:29.010
I'll bring your meal first.

09:30.530 --> 09:32.060
You two look young

09:32.370 --> 09:33.300
and delicate.

09:33.650 --> 09:35.340
Why come to this freezing place?

09:38.460 --> 09:40.250
To see the snowy scenery.

09:40.580 --> 09:41.420
See the scenery?

09:41.980 --> 09:43.420
This blizzard

09:44.010 --> 09:45.890
is hardly a good time to sightsee.

09:45.980 --> 09:46.820
Is that so?

09:49.890 --> 09:51.580
I'll set the dishes for you.

09:52.850 --> 09:53.770
Thanks, ma'am.

09:56.060 --> 09:57.530
It's too hot!

09:59.890 --> 10:00.730
Sorry.

10:00.730 --> 10:01.570
I'm sorry.

10:01.890 --> 10:02.770
Sorry to disturb you.

10:03.370 --> 10:04.220
Sorry.

10:04.250 --> 10:05.090
I'm sorry.

10:06.490 --> 10:07.330
Sorry.

10:07.580 --> 10:08.460
Sorry to disturb you.

10:08.890 --> 10:10.220
I'm too clumsy.

10:12.370 --> 10:14.100
(Qinong)
Are you also here for the saliva?

10:15.130 --> 10:16.100
What saliva?

10:16.850 --> 10:18.940
The saliva of the Snow-Scale Beast.

10:19.420 --> 10:21.730
It's said the long-lost Snow-Scale Beast

10:21.730 --> 10:23.060
is about to appear.

10:23.610 --> 10:25.610
Its saliva can repair internal energy

10:25.610 --> 10:26.530
and grant longevity.

10:26.940 --> 10:28.180
My master is weak,

10:28.650 --> 10:30.370
so we're hoping for some luck.

10:30.700 --> 10:31.980
Qinong.

10:32.610 --> 10:33.730
I need to go back.

10:44.770 --> 10:45.610
Slow down.

10:45.820 --> 10:46.660
Wan Dazhuang?

10:48.370 --> 10:49.460
Eyes frozen

10:49.460 --> 10:50.340
on the beauty?

11:03.340 --> 11:04.250
Miss,

11:05.100 --> 11:06.610
this place isn't safe.

11:07.100 --> 11:08.490
Do you want us

11:08.730 --> 11:09.850
to scout the path?

11:10.220 --> 11:11.180
Go away!

11:39.530 --> 11:40.370
You...

11:41.460 --> 11:42.300
It wasn't me.

11:45.060 --> 11:45.900
It was me.

12:16.060 --> 12:17.530
I've looked for you for so long.

12:23.610 --> 12:24.850
Why betray me

12:25.010 --> 12:26.250
and elope with this pretty boy?

12:29.580 --> 12:30.460
Sir,

12:30.940 --> 12:32.610
your attack is so cruel.

12:33.100 --> 12:34.980
Though their behavior was wrong,

12:35.180 --> 12:36.340
they didn't deserve death.

12:38.820 --> 12:39.660
You...

12:45.890 --> 12:46.730
Everyone,

12:48.850 --> 12:51.850
those two are notorious rapists
in the northwest,

12:52.180 --> 12:54.193
killing dozens of women.

12:54.204 --> 12:55.369
(Zhou Zhiqin, Peiqiong Manor)

12:55.380 --> 12:56.490
They deserved

12:57.220 --> 12:58.580
such deaths.

12:59.700 --> 13:01.770
This is Uncle Zhou's cousin.

13:02.220 --> 13:03.490
I saw him as a child.

13:05.490 --> 13:07.460
Are you from Peiqiong Manor?

13:08.460 --> 13:09.850
I'm Zhou Zhiqin.

13:11.220 --> 13:12.300
May I ask

13:13.010 --> 13:14.100
your name?

13:14.530 --> 13:15.420
I am

13:17.100 --> 13:17.940
Yan Ning.

13:18.980 --> 13:20.610
Thanks for your help, Mr. Zhou.

13:25.580 --> 13:26.980
You're my fiancée,

13:27.940 --> 13:29.490
yet you ran off with my heirloom

13:29.940 --> 13:31.820
and this pretty boy.

13:32.180 --> 13:33.220
Surely, I'd look for you.

13:34.060 --> 13:35.370
Who took your heirloom?

13:35.370 --> 13:37.180
Wait. Who is your fiancée?

13:37.250 --> 13:39.010
I'm not the pretty boy either.

13:40.580 --> 13:42.250
Isn't this my heirloom,

13:42.250 --> 13:43.940
the scale of the Snow-Scale Beast?

13:47.820 --> 13:48.700
What a pity.

13:49.010 --> 13:50.890
The pretty boy defiled it.

13:53.580 --> 13:54.546
I don't want it anymore.

13:58.690 --> 13:59.540
I want it.

14:00.050 --> 14:00.910
Give it to me!

14:01.130 --> 14:02.190
Mine!

14:02.610 --> 14:03.550
Mine!

14:05.980 --> 14:06.850
Played enough?

14:08.850 --> 14:10.250
Just some Jianghu punks.

14:11.060 --> 14:12.730
They can hardly fight.

14:13.100 --> 14:14.250
Except for Mr. Zhou,

14:14.700 --> 14:15.700
they're nothing.

14:17.010 --> 14:19.530
Those three haven't acted yet.

14:28.490 --> 14:30.820
Why did your Uncle Zhou
also want the scale?

14:31.530 --> 14:32.580
I don't know.

14:33.180 --> 14:34.370
This is enough.

14:41.890 --> 14:43.340
No wonder it's a family heirloom.

14:43.370 --> 14:45.730
I heard the Snow-Scale Beast
can sense this scale.

14:46.650 --> 14:47.700
Losing it would be a shame.

14:49.300 --> 14:50.340
Why not lend it to me?

14:51.530 --> 14:53.980
Dazhuang has been weak since childhood.

14:54.340 --> 14:55.759
I want to secure the saliva for him.

14:57.010 --> 14:58.890
So, it is for the pretty boy.

15:04.980 --> 15:05.820
Mr. Yan,

15:06.370 --> 15:08.180
my son had an accident here last year.

15:09.530 --> 15:10.850
The guards who escaped said

15:11.610 --> 15:13.420
he encountered the Snow-Scale Beast

15:13.700 --> 15:14.540
and died.

15:15.460 --> 15:17.180
I just want to retrieve his body

15:17.420 --> 15:18.420
for a proper burial.

15:19.490 --> 15:20.700
Please, Mr. Yan,

15:21.340 --> 15:22.250
lend me the scale.

15:23.300 --> 15:24.190
Give it to me.

15:24.200 --> 15:25.690
- Give it to me.
- Mr. Yan.

15:25.850 --> 15:26.690
Give it to me.

15:27.373 --> 15:28.748
- Give it to me.
- I need it, too.

15:28.759 --> 15:29.540
Mr. Yan.

15:30.700 --> 15:31.540
Good.

15:31.980 --> 15:33.130
Once we find the saliva,

15:33.730 --> 15:35.250
you'll come back with me.

15:37.010 --> 15:38.010
Tomorrow morning,

15:38.340 --> 15:39.650
let's set off

15:40.460 --> 15:41.820
to find the saliva.

15:42.180 --> 15:43.220
Okay.

15:47.940 --> 15:50.300
Where did you get the scale?

15:51.300 --> 15:52.220
The Jiuzhou Archive.

15:54.180 --> 15:55.220
Does it have slime?

15:55.420 --> 15:56.580
That kind of substance

15:56.850 --> 15:57.956
does not congeal in the cold

15:58.060 --> 15:58.980
and melts when heated.

15:59.820 --> 16:01.460
The archive
hasn't been cleaned for ages.

16:01.650 --> 16:02.843
So, it couldn't be preserved.

16:03.676 --> 16:05.089
Are we really going up the mountain

16:05.100 --> 16:06.370
with those people tomorrow?

16:06.700 --> 16:07.973
The enemy is better in the open

16:08.180 --> 16:09.180
than in the dark.

16:11.940 --> 16:13.490
Why did you chase after us?

16:16.130 --> 16:17.940
You stole my Peng.

16:18.723 --> 16:20.010
Of course, I had to get it back.

16:24.730 --> 16:25.570
Sleeping powder?

16:48.100 --> 16:49.010
The landlady?

16:50.130 --> 16:51.650
Why sneak in

16:52.060 --> 16:53.060
at night?

16:54.300 --> 16:55.560
The snow mountains have spirits.

16:55.940 --> 16:57.370
Trespassers won't fare well.

16:57.820 --> 16:58.700
I advise you two

16:58.850 --> 16:59.890
to return the way you came

17:00.530 --> 17:02.100
to save your lives.

17:03.300 --> 17:04.373
You must be very familiar

17:04.620 --> 17:06.290
with the snowy mountains.

17:06.900 --> 17:07.740
Better stay

17:08.180 --> 17:09.140
and guide us.

17:19.420 --> 17:20.700
Hidden elites.

17:21.620 --> 17:22.460
Interesting.

17:52.250 --> 17:53.220
You're still sick.

17:53.860 --> 17:54.730
Why come here?

17:58.940 --> 18:00.366
Are you worried about that Cai girl?

18:01.232 --> 18:02.702
If not for fearing I'd slow her down,

18:03.530 --> 18:04.620
I would go with her.

18:06.570 --> 18:08.810
Zhao is not simple.

18:09.530 --> 18:11.900
She might bring back the antidote.

18:12.220 --> 18:13.060
Yuzhi,

18:13.620 --> 18:16.490
you've never seemed to care
so much about Lingbo.

18:18.860 --> 18:19.810
Master is in danger;

18:20.290 --> 18:21.530
the sect is in peril.

18:22.050 --> 18:23.460
Yet you still have time for jokes?

18:25.380 --> 18:26.290
Don't worry.

18:26.660 --> 18:27.500
With me here,

18:28.420 --> 18:30.530
Qingque Sect won't fall into chaos.

19:44.530 --> 19:45.940
I'm still here.

20:10.220 --> 20:11.420
There's not even a direction.

20:11.900 --> 20:13.090
Where do we start looking?

20:13.570 --> 20:14.460
Elder Tianji,

20:16.180 --> 20:17.330
let's find a place to rest.

20:17.730 --> 20:18.570
Alright.

20:19.220 --> 20:21.290
Everyone, rest up ahead.

20:21.700 --> 20:22.540
Let's go.

20:30.530 --> 20:31.370
Qian Xueshen,

20:31.700 --> 20:33.050
why so quiet today?

20:33.490 --> 20:35.010
That's unusual.

20:38.900 --> 20:40.140
Where's Mr. Zhang trailing us?

20:40.530 --> 20:41.460
Who saw him?

20:48.700 --> 20:49.540
Something's wrong.

20:50.490 --> 20:51.570
We just came this way.

20:51.900 --> 20:53.090
I've seen this stone.

20:53.530 --> 20:54.730
We're back here again.

20:56.570 --> 20:57.460
A ghost maze?

21:00.940 --> 21:02.140
What a mess.

21:02.220 --> 21:03.220
When we first came here,

21:03.420 --> 21:04.260
we went straight...

21:07.660 --> 21:08.500
It's a maze.

21:08.730 --> 21:09.930
Everyone, line up,

21:10.010 --> 21:10.850
one after another.

21:11.250 --> 21:12.220
Try not to get separated.

21:12.700 --> 21:13.860
This...

21:13.860 --> 21:14.710
It's getting dark.

21:14.720 --> 21:16.420
With a ghost maze, we'll never get out.

21:17.380 --> 21:18.700
We'll either freeze

21:18.700 --> 21:19.810
or starve to death here.

21:31.280 --> 21:32.719
Where there's a will, there's a way.

21:32.730 --> 21:33.730
As long as we follow it,

21:33.770 --> 21:34.900
we can escape the maze.

21:35.090 --> 21:35.930
Move.

21:37.220 --> 21:38.060
Come on.

21:45.530 --> 21:47.010
Unordinary fingers.

21:47.290 --> 21:48.140
He knows palm kills

21:51.140 --> 21:52.900
and can break the ice with inner power

21:53.290 --> 21:54.250
to break the maze.

21:55.420 --> 21:56.700
Who is he?

22:03.380 --> 22:04.220
There's a house.

22:04.710 --> 22:06.239
Everyone, get inside to avoid the snow.

22:06.250 --> 22:07.090
Let's go.

22:16.380 --> 22:17.220
Hurry.

22:17.420 --> 22:18.260
Come on.

22:20.050 --> 22:20.890
Follow closely.

22:39.250 --> 22:40.940
This place has been abandoned for years.

22:53.900 --> 22:54.900
Shu?

23:00.810 --> 23:01.770
You two,

23:02.220 --> 23:03.940
find a place to sleep.

23:45.010 --> 23:46.380
Time to eat.

23:48.900 --> 23:50.620
He's truly exhausted.

24:01.220 --> 24:02.180
He won't get cold.

24:10.220 --> 24:11.330
This trip

24:11.900 --> 24:13.220
is undoubtedly perilous.

24:14.140 --> 24:15.660
Are you really going to accompany me?

24:19.250 --> 24:20.660
Though you're heartless toward me,

24:22.490 --> 24:23.900
I can't do the same to you.

24:38.660 --> 24:39.810
That old servant

24:41.140 --> 24:42.620
reminds me of someone.

24:45.620 --> 24:46.460
Who?

24:46.810 --> 24:48.596
Another adopted son
of my great-grandfather,

24:49.330 --> 24:50.380
Elder Tianji,

24:50.770 --> 24:51.610
Duan Jiuxiu.

24:53.980 --> 24:55.530
He and Nie Hengcheng were both adopted.

24:56.290 --> 24:57.980
Why was Nie Hengcheng the Chief,

24:58.700 --> 24:59.813
while he was just an elder?

25:01.290 --> 25:02.460
So, he couldn't accept it.

25:04.050 --> 25:06.250
16 years ago,
the Lord of Qingfeng Temple

25:06.420 --> 25:07.980
mocked him as the eternal second.

25:08.420 --> 25:10.140
He slaughtered the entire temple

25:11.050 --> 25:12.660
and even turned young novices under ten

25:13.380 --> 25:14.620
into human fodder.

25:19.980 --> 25:22.420
Later, your aunt issued a Death Warrant.

25:22.960 --> 25:23.810
It's said

25:23.810 --> 25:25.620
he died in a ruined temple.

25:40.940 --> 25:42.660
The footprint of the Snow-Scale Beast.

25:45.940 --> 25:46.900
Congratulations, Master.

25:46.900 --> 25:48.100
Move, move!

25:49.180 --> 25:50.020
Let's go!

26:03.570 --> 26:05.250
It's the Jade Statue.

26:07.220 --> 26:08.810
The flowers on the base look

26:09.250 --> 26:11.730
like the tri-colored peach blossoms
unique to Luoying Valley.

26:13.220 --> 26:14.620
Could she be Gu Qingkong?

26:14.980 --> 26:15.900
In the wilderness,

26:16.220 --> 26:17.810
who put this statue here?

27:01.770 --> 27:02.730
All dead.

27:07.380 --> 27:08.490
Dead for over six months.

27:14.660 --> 27:15.500
There's a hole here.

27:15.880 --> 27:16.720
A hole?

27:34.090 --> 27:34.930
Wait.

27:37.570 --> 27:38.610
There's something inside.

27:49.940 --> 27:50.810
A snake!

27:50.810 --> 27:52.050
A huge snake!

28:01.810 --> 28:03.180
Qian Xueshen!

28:26.570 --> 28:27.700
The Red-Eyed Crystal Python,

28:27.900 --> 28:28.740
an ancient beast.

28:29.036 --> 28:30.632
Its breath can connect to the underworld

28:30.643 --> 28:31.530
and freeze everything.

28:31.700 --> 28:32.550
Zhao,

28:32.570 --> 28:33.410
stay close to me.

28:33.940 --> 28:34.780
Alright.

28:39.250 --> 28:40.090
Run!

28:45.380 --> 28:46.220
Qian Xueshen!

29:18.180 --> 29:19.020
Go!

29:46.456 --> 29:47.460
I thought you'd care less

29:47.460 --> 29:48.730
about life and death

29:49.250 --> 29:51.620
after the Qingque Sect massacre.

29:52.940 --> 29:54.700
Qian Xueshen came with me.

29:56.420 --> 29:57.530
He's not evil.

29:58.090 --> 29:59.330
If he falls into the hands

29:59.330 --> 30:00.220
of the Demonic Camp,

30:00.490 --> 30:01.460
after they use him,

30:02.180 --> 30:03.140
he'll be dead anyway.

30:04.810 --> 30:05.980
Jianghu is like this.

30:07.290 --> 30:08.980
Only ruthlessness ensures survival.

30:10.180 --> 30:11.290
If you're not ruthless,

30:12.810 --> 30:14.700
you'll end up like Qian Xueshen.

30:16.420 --> 30:17.260
Yulin,

30:18.460 --> 30:19.380
I'm here.

30:20.380 --> 30:22.050
I'll take you home.

30:34.460 --> 30:36.290
That's Zhou Zhiqin's son, Zhou Yulin.

30:42.330 --> 30:43.170
Yulin...

30:43.290 --> 30:45.330
- Mr. Zhou found his son.
- Yulin.

30:52.860 --> 30:53.700
That is...

30:54.420 --> 30:56.940
(Mr. Zhou wants the saliva for himself.)

30:58.050 --> 30:58.890
Jiu,

30:59.860 --> 31:01.460
go help Mr. Zhou.

31:01.460 --> 31:02.300
Yes.

31:11.460 --> 31:12.300
Don't come near.

31:13.330 --> 31:14.380
I don't need your help.

31:15.180 --> 31:16.490
I'll take Yulin back myself.

31:17.770 --> 31:20.530
Better let me help you.

31:52.490 --> 31:54.140
Is this the Snow-Scale Beast's saliva?

31:54.860 --> 31:56.090
Return it.

32:10.050 --> 32:10.890
Mr. Zhou.

32:12.420 --> 32:13.260
Mr. Zhou.

32:14.220 --> 32:15.530
That belongs to Yulin.

32:16.250 --> 32:17.330
Don't give it to him.

32:19.980 --> 32:21.050
Take Mr. Zhou away.

32:21.719 --> 32:23.252
We'll meet at the foot of the mountain.

32:24.140 --> 32:25.140
I'll wait there for you.

32:39.570 --> 32:40.490
Elder Tianji.

32:44.220 --> 32:45.290
Kid.

32:45.700 --> 32:47.260
(Duan Jiuxiu, Elder Tianji)
Sharp eyes.

32:47.290 --> 32:49.050
You recognized me.

32:51.410 --> 32:53.140
You were once Elder Tianji,

32:54.180 --> 32:55.810
but now you're reduced

32:56.700 --> 32:57.900
to following behind,

32:58.140 --> 32:59.090
acting as a servant.

32:59.490 --> 33:01.570
Truly tragic.

33:02.380 --> 33:03.860
You're asking for death.

33:08.090 --> 33:09.380
I heard that one is the weakest

33:09.380 --> 33:10.730
among Nie Hengcheng's

33:11.090 --> 33:12.490
four disciples.

33:13.530 --> 33:15.900
He survived only

33:16.810 --> 33:18.700
by flattering Nie Zhe daily.

33:19.770 --> 33:20.610
I think

33:21.140 --> 33:22.810
it must be you, Chen Shu.

33:22.810 --> 33:24.810
(Chen Shu, Li Sect)

33:24.810 --> 33:26.940
You know too much.

33:27.090 --> 33:28.810
I think you've grown tired of living.

33:28.810 --> 33:30.140
Who are you?

33:30.860 --> 33:31.700
Who am I?

33:32.050 --> 33:33.050
I'm your ancestor.

33:38.660 --> 33:39.620
Wudu Palm.

33:40.660 --> 33:42.180
You recognize it.

33:42.770 --> 33:44.700
You're of the Li Sect?

33:45.050 --> 33:46.220
As a Li Sect member,

33:47.280 --> 33:48.730
how dare you covet the Ziwei Method,

33:48.730 --> 33:49.620
wanting to practice it?

33:51.010 --> 33:52.620
If Nie Zhe knew,

33:53.250 --> 33:54.483
your bones would be gouged out,

33:54.770 --> 33:55.810
and you'd be beheaded.

33:56.220 --> 33:57.420
How arrogant

33:57.420 --> 33:58.900
before death.

34:15.260 --> 34:16.333
(His skills are so strong.)

34:16.530 --> 34:17.820
(He should be able to escape.)

34:19.130 --> 34:19.970
No.

34:20.980 --> 34:21.940
I must help him.

34:24.210 --> 34:25.050
Miss Feng.

34:26.010 --> 34:26.940
Miss Feng.

34:32.650 --> 34:33.490
Mr. Zhou,

34:33.820 --> 34:34.660
how are you?

34:38.740 --> 34:40.170
Thanks to your medicine,

34:40.740 --> 34:41.580
I'm much better.

34:41.860 --> 34:42.700
Thank you.

34:43.900 --> 34:45.130
Then rest a bit.

34:45.690 --> 34:47.260
We'll leave first.

34:47.780 --> 34:49.610
I, as a father, have failed.

34:50.300 --> 34:51.650
I can't take my son home

34:52.090 --> 34:53.490
and have to leave him alone

34:53.490 --> 34:55.210
in this snow-covered mountain.

34:57.170 --> 34:59.010
You must protect the saliva.

34:59.300 --> 35:02.980
It's my son's last item for me.

35:06.400 --> 35:07.980
Mr. Zhou, young lady,

35:07.980 --> 35:08.820
you two are here.

35:08.980 --> 35:10.133
We've looked for a long time.

35:10.340 --> 35:11.180
Where are they?

35:14.380 --> 35:15.420
Your lover

35:15.780 --> 35:16.620
stubbornly refused

35:16.860 --> 35:17.700
to leave

35:18.420 --> 35:19.420
and was swallowed

35:20.130 --> 35:21.010
by the python

35:22.780 --> 35:23.900
with Jiu.

35:31.740 --> 35:32.650
He's dead?

35:33.780 --> 35:35.210
The python was too fierce.

35:35.530 --> 35:37.460
Its icy breath killed him instantly.

35:38.090 --> 35:40.050
What a pity for the cute young man.

35:40.820 --> 35:41.780
My condolences.

35:48.610 --> 35:49.450
Young lady,

35:50.690 --> 35:52.090
you still have the saliva, right?

35:52.650 --> 35:54.170
Jiu was wrong to take it,

35:54.460 --> 35:56.380
but this saliva is vital to our master.

35:56.650 --> 35:58.460
Now, it's useless for you.

35:58.820 --> 35:59.753
Why not sell it to us?

36:00.260 --> 36:01.100
Set a price.

36:01.900 --> 36:02.740
A thousand gold?

36:02.940 --> 36:04.430
Miss Feng, don't listen to them.

36:04.460 --> 36:05.300
They are bad people.

36:05.820 --> 36:06.940
Once we restrain them,

36:07.490 --> 36:08.636
we'll go find your companion.

36:30.010 --> 36:30.940
Sunshine Blade...

36:33.650 --> 36:34.530
You are Cai Zhao?

36:35.090 --> 36:35.930
Uncle Zhou,

36:36.740 --> 36:37.650
long time no see

36:37.980 --> 36:39.010
since childhood.

36:39.380 --> 36:40.780
How have you been?

36:41.300 --> 36:42.210
Kid,

36:42.570 --> 36:44.050
why attack me?

36:44.490 --> 36:46.260
My aunt grew up in Peiqiong Manor

36:46.570 --> 36:47.410
and could recognize

36:47.780 --> 36:49.213
the Zhous' swordsmanship blindfolded.

36:49.940 --> 36:51.090
I don't have eyes on my back,

36:51.740 --> 36:53.130
but I saw your shadow.

36:54.090 --> 36:55.300
Your sword

36:55.820 --> 36:57.780
is in the Moonlight Drinking stance,

36:58.490 --> 37:00.530
a close combat technique.

37:01.690 --> 37:03.260
They were so far apart.

37:03.940 --> 37:04.780
Uncle Zhou,

37:05.740 --> 37:07.490
who exactly are you trying to kill?

37:08.340 --> 37:09.210
Actually, I...

37:09.210 --> 37:10.170
I felt it was strange

37:10.860 --> 37:11.980
in the ice cave.

37:12.260 --> 37:13.460
Seeing the corpse of your kin,

37:13.780 --> 37:14.980
you kept digging in his hands.

37:19.300 --> 37:20.170
You didn't come

37:20.860 --> 37:23.010
for your son

37:24.010 --> 37:25.570
but for the saliva.

37:26.420 --> 37:27.690
That is Yulin's item.

37:27.860 --> 37:29.740
Zhao, if I wanted to harm you,

37:30.050 --> 37:32.090
why did I risk my life to protect you?

37:32.090 --> 37:33.490
That was the reason

37:34.340 --> 37:35.650
that I dismissed my doubts.

37:36.420 --> 37:37.780
That's why I healed you.

37:37.940 --> 37:38.860
Now, I see.

37:39.170 --> 37:40.940
It was just a ruse.

37:41.570 --> 37:42.410
Zhao,

37:42.980 --> 37:44.340
we are both from the Six Sects.

37:44.340 --> 37:45.690
I was friends with your aunt.

37:45.720 --> 37:46.570
Why say this?

37:46.570 --> 37:47.860
That's exactly why

37:47.860 --> 37:49.300
I didn't want to believe it,

37:50.980 --> 37:52.130
but just now,

37:52.940 --> 37:54.340
I had no choice but to confirm.

37:55.610 --> 37:58.420
You schemed for the saliva.

37:58.860 --> 38:00.650
What exactly do you want with it?

38:04.193 --> 38:05.460
Young lady, what are you doing?

38:05.460 --> 38:06.940
I heard saliva melts in fire.

38:07.460 --> 38:08.420
If Uncle Zhou

38:08.690 --> 38:09.780
doesn't explain today,

38:10.340 --> 38:11.260
I'll destroy it

38:12.460 --> 38:14.130
to keep it from falling into evil hands.

38:15.570 --> 38:16.900
Zhou Zhiqin, tell her!

38:19.130 --> 38:20.420
I did it for Jianghu's safety,

38:20.980 --> 38:22.050
bearing humiliation,

38:22.380 --> 38:24.050
mingling with these demon sect people,

38:24.090 --> 38:25.736
to prevent them
from practicing evil arts

38:26.376 --> 38:27.380
and endangering everyone.

38:28.980 --> 38:29.820
Evil arts?

38:30.210 --> 38:31.940
It's called the Ziwei Method.

38:32.420 --> 38:33.650
This method

38:33.650 --> 38:34.570
was powerful

38:34.690 --> 38:35.570
and invincible.

38:36.095 --> 38:37.562
Later, Nie Hengcheng somehow acquired

38:37.573 --> 38:38.940
its cultivation method,

38:39.300 --> 38:41.090
and it became the root of all disasters.

38:41.690 --> 38:45.420
So, practicing the Ziwei Method
needs the saliva.

38:47.820 --> 38:49.010
What Ziwei Method?

38:49.530 --> 38:50.370
I don't know.

38:51.170 --> 38:52.130
Careful!

38:54.860 --> 38:55.980
Did Zhou Zhiqin work with you

38:56.050 --> 38:57.260
for the Ziwei Method?

39:03.300 --> 39:04.140
Correct.

39:04.460 --> 39:05.980
My master Nie Hengcheng

39:05.980 --> 39:08.610
only reached the third layer

39:08.820 --> 39:10.130
and was already invincible.

39:10.820 --> 39:12.610
Mr. Zhou wants to practice it,

39:12.610 --> 39:15.090
obviously to become
the Lord of Peiqiong Manor,

39:15.090 --> 39:17.780
so he worked with Elder Tianji and me.

39:18.010 --> 39:19.050
Is that right,

39:20.740 --> 39:21.610
Mr. Zhou?

39:22.940 --> 39:24.900
Duan Jiuxiu, Elder Tianji

39:26.010 --> 39:27.690
was already killed by my aunt.

39:27.940 --> 39:29.490
Why is he still alive?

39:36.241 --> 39:46.901
=Generation to Generation=

40:05.661 --> 40:10.071
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

40:10.636 --> 40:15.251
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

40:15.591 --> 40:20.156
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

40:20.681 --> 40:24.981
♪Free to wander in the world♪

40:27.926 --> 40:32.626
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

40:33.151 --> 40:37.441
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

40:38.101 --> 40:42.131
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

40:42.446 --> 40:47.571
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

40:48.146 --> 40:52.956
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

40:53.171 --> 40:57.341
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

40:58.066 --> 41:02.001
♪I freely roam in the world♪

41:02.501 --> 41:07.776
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

41:30.506 --> 41:35.636
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

41:36.001 --> 41:40.371
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

41:40.636 --> 41:44.766
♪I freely roam in the world♪

41:44.951 --> 41:50.526
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
